      "text": "Y&W",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 10.43,
      "time_str": "00:10.430",
      "text": "一杯二锅头呛得眼泪流",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 15.5,
      "time_str": "00:15.500",
      "text": "生旦净末丑好汉不回头",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 19.96,
      "time_str": "00:19.960",
      "text": "你若要走我不会留",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 25.03,
      "time_str": "00:25.030",
      "text": "强留的爱情不会撑得太久",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 30.15,
      "time_str": "00:30.150",
      "text": "不耐寂寞尺度游走",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 35.26,
      "time_str": "00:35.260",
      "text": "别以为地下恋情密不透风",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 40.51,
      "time_str": "00:40.510",
      "text": "我说算你狠善用无辜的眼神",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 45.7,
      "time_str": "00:45.700",
      "text": "谎话说了两次我就当真",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 51.13,
      "time_str": "00:51.130",
      "text": "我说算我笨软不隆咚的耳根",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 56.0,
      "time_str": "00:56.000",
      "text": "只为一时的气氛搞一肚子的气愤ya~",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 62.07,
      "time_str": "01:02.070",
      "text": "一看到你我就想到过去",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 64.2,
      "time_str": "01:04.200",
      "text": "就立刻让我血冲到脑子里去",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 66.86,
      "time_str": "01:06.860",
      "text": "我的心里只会永远的恨你",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 71.88,
      "time_str": "01:11.880",
      "text": "你跟别人吃香又喝辣去",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 74.54,
      "time_str": "01:14.540",
      "text": "丢我一个人在这里吹冷空气",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 77.1,
      "time_str": "01:17.100",
      "text": "我会活得很好真的没关系",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 82.56,
      "time_str": "01:22.560",
      "text": "你真是没什么良心把我就这样抛弃",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 92.94,
      "time_str": "01:32.940",
      "text": "我真是没什么出息对你还放不下去",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 102.66,
      "time_str": "01:42.660",
      "text": "喝什么酒解什么愁",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 107.6,
      "time_str": "01:47.600",
      "text": "喝一杯\"请你走路\"不必回头",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 112.75,
      "time_str": "01:52.750",
      "text": "午夜过后酒吧门口",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 117.91,
      "time_str": "01:57.910",
      "text": "我走了以免爱又飞来横祸",
